{
  "texts": [
    "Image caption generation technology can accurately describe the diseases affecting crops, enhance the precision of disease identification, aid in early detection and diagnosis of plant diseases, and minimize crop losses.",
    "It can also be integrated with other agricultural intelligence technologies, such as drones and sensors, to achieve automatic monitoring and management of farmland.",
    "This integration can enable farmers and agricultural practitioners to accurately identify diseases through image capture, even without expertise in disease identification.",
    "This will help reduce the barrier to identifying diseases and promote the adoption and application of agricultural technology.",
    "However, the model we propose still has certain limitations."
  ]
}